item.title: How to make $$$ on YouTube in 2023 - with Rohan Sheth
item.description:
Is there a surefire way to make money on social media, in particular YouTube, in 2023?

Well... no. But Rohan Sheth has built several profiles that have generated 7-figures in online sales across several channels. He runs a successful video marketing agency that obsesses over how to reach the largest (and most profitable) audience possible, regardless of industry or niche.


This conversation explores what it takes to make money with YouTube... Feed: https://feeds.captivate.fm/maria-sparagis/
